com.interpss.core.algo.planning

Interface PlanningAclfNetwork

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfNetwork, BaseAclfNetwork<AclfBus,AclfBranch>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAreaZone, IAclfNetAdjustment, IAclfNetElement, IAclfNetFormMatrix, IAclfNetFunc, IAclfNetLookup, IChildNet, INet3WXfrElement, NameTag, Network<AclfBus,AclfBranch>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PlanningAclfNetworkImpl

    public interface PlanningAclfNetwork
extends AclfNetwork
    A representation of the model object 'Net Container'. Planning time period AclfNetwork object container class. 1) The changeBus/Branch/SubList contain all relevent/known planning chnages. 2) The start/endTime are for defining planning study interval. The study interval consists of multiple time periods.

    The following features are supported:

    • Start Time
    • End Time
    • Change Bus List
    • Change Branch List
    • Change Sub List
    • Plan Period Aclf Net List
    See Also:
    PlanningAlgorithmPackage.getPlanningAclfNetwork()
